      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! It's the perfect fit for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great pulling into the driveway. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love how it handles!",
