    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six. This unit delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically robust, the ZF 6-speed manual transmission provides precise engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's known lateral stress points. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its 'good' classification, the suspension geometry is dialed, and the braking system retains firm hydraulic pressure. A true enthusiast's specimen optimized for longitudinal and lateral performance.",
